00:06.707 --> 00:09.276 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
On the "NewsHour" tonight:
tragedy in Berlin.

00:09.309 --> 00:15.148 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
At least nine people are dead
and many others
injured after a truck plowed
into a Christmas

00:15.182 --> 00:16.149 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
market.

00:16.183 --> 00:18.285 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
