After days of delays,
evacuations resume in
the war ravaged Syrian city of
Aleppo.

00:24.191 --> 00:30.964 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Then: Protests greet Electoral
College voters
as they gather at statehouses
across the country

00:30.998 --> 00:34.134 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to finalize president-elect
Trump's win.

00:34.167 --> 00:38.572 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Our Politics Monday duo analyze
the latest
in the transition.

00:38.605 --> 00:44.111 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Plus: a rare look inside Bruce
Springsteen's
personal studio.

00:44.144 --> 00:47.414 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
