his creative
process.

00:47.447 --> 00:52.953 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BRUCE SPRINGSTEEN, Musician:
Most artists
I know consider themselves to be
phonies,

00:52.986 --> 00:57.891 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
along with the feeling that
there's something
that you're doing is essential,
essential

00:57.925 --> 01:03.830 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to communicate, and deeply,
deeply real.

01:03.864 --> 01:07.567 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: All that and more
on tonight's
"PBS NewsHour."

01:07.601 --> 01:10.771 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
(BREAK)

01:10.804 --> 01:25.085 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: It's been a day
of horror in
the capital cities of Germany
and Turkey.

01:25.118 --> 01:29.723 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
First Berlin, where a truck
drove into a crowd
of Christmas shoppers, leaving
the street

01:29.756 --> 01:31.825 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
full of dead and wounded.

01:31.858 --> 01:33.760 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
We get more now from Ira
Spitzer.

01:33.794 --> 01:37.230 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He's the Berlin bureau chief for
Feature Story
News.

01:37.264 --> 01:40.968 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And a warning: Some images might
be disturbing
to some viewers.

01:41.001 --> 01:46.340 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Let me start, Ira Spitzer, with
this comment
we just saw crossing the wires.

01:46.373 --> 01:52.946 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that is the German interior
minister saying
that more information now does
seem to point

01:52.980 --> 01:54.281 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to an act of terrorism.

01:54.314 --> 01:56.049 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
What do you know?

01:56.083 --> 02:01.788 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
IRA SPITZER, Feature Story News:
Well, the
Berlin police have confirmed
that nine people

02:01.822 --> 02:07.928 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
have been killed in the scene of
violence
earlier in Berlin, and one of
those -- one

02:07.961 --> 02:11.231 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
of the dead was a passenger in
that truck.

02:11.264 --> 02:18.839 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In addition to the nine people
who died, at
least 50 others are injured,
some seriously.

02:18.872 --> 02:25.112 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, the -- as you mentioned
there, the German
interior minister saying that
there are signs

02:25.145 --> 02:27.347 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
here that point to a terror
attack.

02:27.381 --> 02:34.955 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
No one has come out and
explicitly said that
this was intentional, but we
also heard from

02:34.988 --> 02:41.361 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
-- the White House issued a
statement not
long ago, and they also
referenced that this

02:41.395 --> 02:45.032 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
was possibly a terror attack.

02:45.065 --> 02:52.439 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, investigations are ongoing
here in Berlin,
trying to uncover what happened,
but an important

02:52.472 --> 02:58.578 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
piece of information here, the
driver, the
suspected driver of the truck
has been taken

02:58.612 --> 03:00.347 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
into custody.

03:00.380 --> 03:05.685 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So much, of course, will hinge
on who that
person is and what they are able
to uncover

03:05.719 --> 03:07.320 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
from him.

03:07.354 --> 03:10.524 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But, at the moment, police have
asked people
to stay off the streets in
Berlin.

03:10.557 --> 03:15.929 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There is an ongoing rescue
operation that's
happened at a Christmas market
right near

03:15.962 --> 03:20.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the heart of Berlin, so a tragic
situation
unfolding right now.

03:20.267 --> 03:24.071 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Ira Spitzer, tell
us a little
bit more about where this
happened.

03:24.104 --> 03:26.073 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
You describe it as a Christmas
market.

03:26.106 --> 03:29.743 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
What exactly was the location,
the situation?

03:29.776 --> 03:38.819 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
IRA SPITZER: So, this happened
in the district
of Charlottenburg, right near
the Gedachtniskirche,

03:38.852 --> 03:41.555 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
which is a famous landmark here
in Berlin.

03:41.588 --> 03:46.793 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It is a church where they have
not repaired
the steeple from World War II,
so it's visited

03:46.827 --> 03:52.566 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
by many tourists throughout the
course of
the year, and this Christmas
market is someplace

03:52.599 --> 03:58.071 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
where thousands of people
congregate in the
month leading up to the holidays
here.

03:58.105 --> 03:59.573 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
People go there with their
families.

03:59.606 --> 04:02.776 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
They eat, drink, do Christmas
shopping.

04:02.809 --> 04:09.249 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, Christmas markets are a very
big tradition
in Germany, a much loved
tradition in Germany.

04:09.282 --> 04:15.555 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And there also has been a lot of
speculation
in the past few months that
perhaps a Christmas

04:15.589 --> 04:18.625 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
market could be the target of a
terror attack.

04:18.658 --> 04:21.928 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So they have stepped up security
across the
board.

04:21.962 --> 04:28.368 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
However, at these open spaces
like this, it
is, of course, very difficult to
predict and

04:28.401 --> 04:31.972 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
then to prevent an attack from
taking place.

04:32.005 --> 04:36.910 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now, again, we don't know a
hundred percent
that this was an intentional
act.

04:36.943 --> 04:40.113 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
However, the authorities are
certainly treating
it as such right now.

04:40.147 --> 04:47.821 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Ira Spitzer
watching this unfolding
story in Berlin for us, thank
you very much.

04:47.854 --> 04:55.795 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
