Berlin incident,
the Russian ambassador to Turkey
was assassinated

04:55.829 --> 04:58.064 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
by a lone gunman in Ankara.

04:58.098 --> 05:03.570 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
