where Russia's
military is heavily involved.

05:09.743 --> 05:12.979 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The gunman later died in a
shoot-out with
police.

05:13.013 --> 05:17.984 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Russian President Vladimir Putin
and Turkey's
President Recep Tayyip Erdogan
condemned the

05:18.018 --> 05:19.786 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
attack.

05:19.819 --> 05:24.257 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
