electoral votes, losing
two defectors in Texas.

05:33.533 --> 05:37.137 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Hillary Clinton lost four
electors in Washington
State.

05:37.170 --> 05:41.841 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Otherwise, it went mostly as
expected, despite
a day of demonstrations.

05:41.875 --> 05:44.077 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
John Yang reports.

05:44.110 --> 05:48.615 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Election Day, part
two.

05:48.648 --> 05:53.420 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In some states, protesters urged
Electoral
College voters to dump
president-elect Trump.

05:53.453 --> 05:55.188 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
In Pennsylvania:

05:55.222 --> 05:58.024 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN: I'm here today because I
feel like
it's the last chance we have to
really save

05:58.058 --> 05:59.025 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
this country.

05:59.059 --> 06:00.927 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
