popular vote.

06:00.961 --> 06:07.434 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I'm hoping we can make some kind
of difference
in the Electoral College.

06:07.467 --> 06:12.005 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: The outcome didn't
change, but
controversy still swirls around
evidence of

06:12.038 --> 06:15.275 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Russian cyber-attacks aimed at
influencing
the election.

06:15.308 --> 06:17.043 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

06:17.077 --> 06:18.945 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN MCCAIN (R), Arizona:
There's no doubt
they were interfering and no
doubt that it

06:18.979 --> 06:20.814 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
