06:20.847 --> 06:26.152 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The question now is, how much
and what damage
and what should the United
States of America

06:26.186 --> 06:27.887 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
do?

06:27.921 --> 06:30.890 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Senator John McCain
and fellow
Republican Lindsey Graham have
now joined

06:30.924 --> 06:35.862 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
