Jack Reed
to call for a special Senate
committee to

06:35.895 --> 06:37.964 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
try to find the answers.

06:37.998 --> 06:43.870 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Senate Majority Leader Mitch
McConnell says
existing panels should handle
the investigation.

06:43.903 --> 06:48.475 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Clinton campaign chairman John
Podesta suggested
Trump aides may have colluded
with Moscow.

06:48.508 --> 06:50.810 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN PODESTA, Former Clinton
Campaign Chairman:
What did Trump, Inc., know and
when did they

06:50.844 --> 06:52.145 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
know it?

06:52.178 --> 06:53.413 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Were they in touch with the
Russians?

06:53.446 --> 06:55.282 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I think those are still open
questions.

06:55.315 --> 06:59.719 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Mr. Trump's incoming
chief of staff
said the president-elect isn't
convinced Russia

06:59.753 --> 07:01.621 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
