show the American

07:10.930 --> 07:15.568 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
people that they're actually on
the same page,
as opposed to third parties
through The Washington

07:15.602 --> 07:17.437 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Post.

07:17.470 --> 07:21.541 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Mr. Trump is spending
the Christmas
holidays at his Mar-a-Lago
resort in Florida.

07:21.574 --> 07:23.677 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
For the "PBS NewsHour," I'm John
Yang.

07:23.710 --> 07:28.281 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
