an unusual
hearing, with no accusation and
no sentence.

08:41.321 --> 08:43.423 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
So, where are we exactly?

08:43.456 --> 08:50.130 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
