commuted the sentences for more
than 1,300

11:31.991 --> 11:35.628 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
people, more than any of his
predecessors.

11:35.662 --> 11:37.797 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Wall Street managed modest gains
today.

11:37.830 --> 11:43.870 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Dow Jones industrial average
