11:48.675 --> 11:53.546 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And Zsa Zsa Gabor died Sunday in
Los Angeles,
after years of ill health.

11:53.580 --> 11:59.085 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The Hungarian-born actress was
known for her
glamorous image and multiple
marriages, including

11:59.118 --> 12:03.489 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to hotel mogul Conrad Hilton in
the 1940s.

12:03.523 --> 12:09.062 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And she made divorce an art
form, once quipping:
