12:09.095 --> 12:11.931 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Every time I leave a man, I keep
his house."

12:11.965 --> 12:15.234 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Zsa Zsa Gabor was 99 years old.

12:15.268 --> 12:20.306 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
