essential to communicate, and
deeply, deeply

42:06.858 --> 42:08.693 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
real.

42:08.726 --> 42:15.466 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Springsteen has
