working-class rock
'n' roll hero to millions of
devoted fans.

42:26.044 --> 42:31.015 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In the recording studio he built
at this rural
New Jersey home, we talked about
becoming

42:31.048 --> 42:35.219 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Bruce Springsteen, the story he
