way to do it, but it was
certainly -- it was

44:04.575 --> 44:06.377 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
the most effective for us.

44:06.410 --> 44:09.213 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: I mean, but you
