44:10.681 --> 44:11.649 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
BRUCE SPRINGSTEEN: Yes.

44:11.682 --> 44:13.451 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Now...

44:13.484 --> 44:15.920 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Well, you're
