46:13.170 --> 46:15.006 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Which means what?

46:15.039 --> 46:19.010 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BRUCE SPRINGSTEEN: What you were
